text: Fame and Fortune is a 1986 studio album by Bad Company. Fame and Fortune may also refer to: * "Fame and Fortune" (Elvis Presley song), 1960 * "Fame and Fortune" (Bad Company song), 1986 * Fame and Fortune (American game show), American game show (1989–1991) * Fame and Fortune (Irish game show), Irish television game show (1996–2006) * Fame and Fortune Weekly, American periodical for children (1905–1929)
